 &#8220;Complex, Uncertain, and Slow&#8221; into one that is &#8220;Simple,=
 Certain, and Fast&#8221; by using technology to make instant offers on hom=
es.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">At least one person sees the vision. Last Tuesday, Ch=
